    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Saute uslehze tam /\nehz to/ kad wiꞥsch Pnuëlū bij\nezzen gahjis; un wiꞥsch klibbo-\na ar favu Zisku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz ne ehd Israëta\nBehrni noDsihfles pee Ziskas Loh-\ntta/lihds schodeen / tapehz / ka\nsebkabam ta Dsihfle pee Ziskas\nohzekta maitata tappa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXXIII. Nodalla.\nJehkabs nodalla sawas Seewas/Behrnuß un\nGaimi treijôs Pulkôs: 1. Pasemmojahs\npreckich sawu Brahli Eesawu : 3. Un tas ilgi\nar sawu Brahli runnajis un sirdigi falih,\nbsinajees. r. Greeschahs atpaklat : 17. Bet\nJehkabs eet us to Semmi Kanään un eezei\ntur to ihsteuu Deewa Kalposhanu : 18 / 20.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N Jehkabs pazehle fa-\nwaz Azzis/ un skatti-\njahs/ un reds / Eesaws\naze/ un tschetrfsimts Wihti ar\nTad peefchihre wiꞥsch tohs\nhrnns pee Leas/ un pee Raë-\nun pee tahm diwi Kalponehin.\n2. Un likke tahs Kalpones un\nanu Behrnus papreeksch / un\ni un winna Behrnus pakkat peemihligt eſti tu mann fannehmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch pats gahje teem\npreekſchâ / un flannijahs feptin-\nreisi pee Semmes/teekams wiꞥsch\npee sawa Brahta klaht tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eesaws tezzeja tam\npretti un apkampeto/ un uettehs\napkahrt winna Kaklu/ un skuhp-\nstija to/ un tee raudaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch pazehle sawas\nAzzis/ un redseja tahs Seewas/\nun tohs Behrmus / un fazzija:\nRam peederr tee/ kas pee tew/ un\ntas fazzija : (schee irr) tee Behr-\nnt / ko Deews tawan Kalpam\nirr eedahwanajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad peegahje tahs Kalpo-\nnes/ winnas/ un winno Behrni/\nun paflannijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lea peegahje arridsan /\nun winnas Behrni / un paftan-\nnijahs / un pehz nahze Jahseps\nun Räele/ un paflannijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch fazzija: Kam\nwiſs tas Lehgeris/ ko es fastap-\npts esin? un tas fazzija: Ka es\nSchehlastibu atrohmu tawas Az-\nzis/ mans Kungs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eesaws fazzija: Man\npascham gann irr/ mans Brah-\nli / paturr / kas tew peederr.\n"
    },
